"{\"uid\": \"dailyhive.com-vancouver-olympic-athletes-cruise-ship-tahiti\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sports  van  Certain Olympic athletes are skipping the traditional village experience for life on a cruise ship.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The surfers at the Paris 2024 Games, who are competing in Tahiti, which is more than 15,000 kilometres away from Paris, will stay on a cruise ship named Aranui 5.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999975315678055, \"rank\": 2.4684382431262717e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999994461632, \"rank\": 5.5383146043985485e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aranui is a cruise company that typically uses this boat for tours around the South Pacific area.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes get their own room as well as have access to common spaces such as a 24-hour dining space, an activity room with ping-pong, and a gift shop, among other amenities.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Japanese athlete Kanoa Igarashi gave a tour of the cruise ship on his TikTok.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9808724539728381, \"rank\": 0.014680434001456256, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kanoa Igarashi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.724825637428042e-25, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the video, you can see some of the common spaces available to athletes, as well as his room.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Non-surfing athletes located back in the Paris Olympic village will be staying onbeds made of cardboard, and they do not look very comfortable.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999994461632, \"rank\": 5.5383146043985485e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The beds on the cruise ship have a traditional mattress, which one would assume would result in a more comfortable experience.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a luxury that has been noted by a few athletes on social media already.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfing has only been included at the Olympics twice, as it made its debut at the Tokyo 2020 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Camilla Kemp, a surfer from Germany, also posted a few videos to TikTok showing off her room on the cruise ship.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairmount_Rowing_Association\", \"score\": 0.8755871075188912, \"rank\": 0.1417659018518462, \"text\": \"Camilla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairmount_Rowing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fairmount_Rowing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\", \"score\": 0.9999387230260205, \"rank\": 6.0741522792887655e-05, \"text\": \"Kemp\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.944485016904004, \"rank\": 0.045998124712836465, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.724825637428042e-25, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kemp also shared this incredible clip of her approaching the big ship, which gives viewers a good idea of its size.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\", \"score\": 0.9999387230260205, \"rank\": 6.0741522792887655e-05, \"text\": \"Kemp\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Kemp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a much different experience than that had by the athletes living in the Paris Olympic village.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9