rt on the globe.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Google Maps  Sanoa Dempfle-Olin, from Tofino, British Columbia, is Canada's lone surfer competing in the event this year.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tofino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.798301786664291e-17, \"text\": \"Tofino\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tofino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tofino\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"score\": 0.9999998902983467, \"rank\": 1.0925791016300215e-07, \"text\": \"British Columbia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\"}, {\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999993434107519, \"rank\": 5.997649191524601e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's the first-ever Canadian surfer to go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.5641026061205833, \"rank\": 0.7110475937464168, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics opening ceremony takes place on Friday, July 26.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2089, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"